FBIS4-20846 "jptac003__l94042" JPRS-TAC-94-003-L JPRS Arms Control 16 March 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Grachev On Nuclear Arsenal Grachev On Nuclear Arsenal `Real Guarantee of Security' LD1603220494 Moscow RIA in English 1932 GMT 16 Mar 94 LD1603220494 Moscow RIA English BFN ["Nuclear forces to get pride of place in development of Russian armed forces - Grachev" -- RIA headline] [Text] Moscow, March 16, RIA -- Defence Minister Pavel Grachev, speaking at a news briefing today, said that in the present conditions it is strategic nuclear forces that are Russia's real guarantee of security, which is stated in the Russian military doctrine.
